headline: LKQ Corporation to Release Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2024 Results on Thursday, February 20, 2025
summary: ANTIOCH, Tenn., Jan. 22, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- LKQ Corporation (Nasdaq: LKQ) will release its fourth quarter and full year 2024 financial results on Thursday, February 20, 2025. Conference Call Details LKQ will host a conference call and webcast on February 20, 2025 at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time (7:00 a.m. Central Time) with members of senior management to discuss the Company's results.
